
		node js respt api.

>setup


	>mkdir nodejs_restapi.

	>cd nodejs_restapi then open in editor(vs code).
	
	>npm init to initialize the creation of package.json file for nodejs project

	>npm i express to install expressjs, with this it will install node_modules for running expressjs

	>create a new file to launch application i.e "app.js", and 
		*(replace index.js in package.json file on main:app.js)

	>use demon service i.e. nodemon watch for changes inside the js file and restart app server

		>sudo npm i -g nodemon,  -g for global, sudo for super user on ubuntu/mac


	>npm i morgan, to see detail of the request for server.




